sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard / CLI)
    participant EvalHub as eval-hub API<br/>8080/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Init as eval-runtime-init<br/>Init Container
    participant Adapter as Adapter Container<br/>(LM Eval / Garak / etc.)
    participant Sidecar as eval-runtime-sidecar<br/>8080/TCP localhost
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,OCI: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Execution

    Client->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SAR)
    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Authenticated & Authorized

    EvalHub->>EvalHub: Store job in DB (PostgreSQL/SQLite)

    opt MLflow enabled
        EvalHub->>MLflow: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/experiments/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        MLflow-->>EvalHub: Experiment ID
    end

    EvalHub->>K8sAPI: Create batch/v1 Job + ConfigMap<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>EvalHub: Job created

    EvalHub-->>Client: 201 Created (Job ID)

    Note over K8sAPI,Adapter: Kubernetes schedules Job Pod

    opt Test data configured
        K8sAPI->>Init: Start init container
        Init->>S3: Download test data<br/>Auth: AWS IAM credentials
        S3-->>Init: Test data artifacts
        Init-->>K8sAPI: Init complete
    end

    K8sAPI->>Adapter: Start adapter + sidecar containers
    K8sAPI->>Sidecar: Start native sidecar (restartPolicy=Always)

    Note over Adapter,Sidecar: Flow 2: Sidecar Auth Token Resolution

    loop For each benchmark
        Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>HTTP localhost:8080 (plaintext)
        Sidecar->>Sidecar: Read SA token from<br/>/var/run/secrets/.../token
        Sidecar->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/evaluations/jobs/{id}/events<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP, Auth: Bearer SA Token
        EvalHub-->>Sidecar: 200 OK
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: 200 OK (proxied)

        opt MLflow enabled
            Adapter->>Sidecar: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-metric<br/>HTTP localhost:8080
            Sidecar->>MLflow: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/log-metric<br/>HTTPS, Auth: Projected SA Token
            MLflow-->>Sidecar: 200 OK
            Sidecar-->>Adapter: 200 OK (proxied)
        end
    end

    opt OCI export enabled
        Adapter->>Sidecar: PUT /v2/{repo}/blobs/uploads<br/>HTTP localhost:8080
        Sidecar->>OCI: PUT /v2/{repo}/blobs/uploads<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, Auth: Docker Registry Token
        OCI-->>Sidecar: 201 Created
        Sidecar-->>Adapter: 201 Created (proxied)
    end

    Adapter->>Sidecar: Final status event (completed/failed)
    Sidecar->>EvalHub: Final status callback<br/>HTTPS 8443/TCP
    EvalHub->>EvalHub: Compute weighted score<br/>Update job state
    EvalHub-->>Sidecar: 200 OK
